Using Theme Gem

1) go to shopify and create a private api
 -> make sure that it has write access
 
2) theme configure api_key password store_domain

3)check config.yml manually

4)theme watch 

---------- When ready to upload the theme to a new a/c ------------

make a copy of all the local files for backup

theme replace

---------To scrape the data from the Big Cartel site ---------------

run the pen/script 

cp & paste the output to a file .csv

https://shop-name.myshopify.com/admin/products -> upload the csv file


